This extension is for use on the Twitter.com web interface. 
It extends the default media previews available for twitpic, youtube, yfrog, etc and adds imgur.com.
It also does partial previews of classified ads on Daft.ie and Adverts.ie.

Currently supported:
- imgur.com
- daft.ie
- adverts.ie

Currently in FF extension sandbox. Couple of small changes required before public release is allowed.

See https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/261946/
